==歷史==
14世纪中[[帕木竹巴政權|帕木竹巴政權]]推行[[宗_(行政區)|宗]][[谿卡|谿]]制度，建岗巴宗，岗巴宗政府設在[[岗巴镇|岗巴宗古堡]]，位于現在的岗巴县城东北面。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xzgb.gov.cn/cgly_1676/201505/t20150505_418316.html |title=岗巴县旅游景点之岗巴古堡 |access-date=2017-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011072231/http://www.xzgb.gov.cn/cgly_1676/201505/t20150505_418316.html |archive-date=2017-10-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>崗巴宗古堡沿著[[石灰岩|石灰岩]]斷崖山勢而建造，俯視周遭平原，有頂的通道通往山下水源，五個圓形[[瓮城|瓮城]]加強對城堡的防守。<ref name="Harrison2012">{{cite book|author=Peter Harrison|title=''Fortress Monasteries of the Himalayas: Tibet, Ladakh, Nepal and Bhutan''| url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lzfDCwAAQBAJ&pg=PT29| date=2012-08-20|publisher=Bloomsbury Publishing|isbn=978-1-78200-190-4|page=第29頁}}</ref><ref name="Harris2012">{{cite book|author=Clare Harris|title=''The Museum on the Roof of the World: Art, Politics, and the Representation of Tibet''|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=N979o0TR4uAC&pg=PA111|date=2012-10-30| publisher=University of Chicago Press| isbn=978-0-226-31747-2| page=第111頁}}</ref>

1903年6月，[[榮赫鵬|榮赫鵬]]上校擔任英國外交使團團長，率領一個由五名軍官、五百名士兵組成的外交使團，從[[錫金|錫金]]翻越[[乃堆拉山口|乃堆拉山口]]到達崗巴宗，要求會晤西藏與清廷代表，談判邊界和通商問題。1903年8月21日，[[第九世班禪喇嘛|第九世班禪喇嘛]]委派的[[扎什倫布寺|扎什倫布寺]]方丈與英國外交使團在崗巴宗會面。在等待西藏與清廷代表五個月後，外交使團無功而返。<ref name="French2016">{{cite book|author=Patrick French| title=''Younghusband: The Last Great Imperial Adventurer''| url=https://books.google.com/books?id=85NbDAAAQBAJ&pg=PT222|date=2016-06-21|publisher=Knopf Doubleday Publishing Group| isbn=978-1-101-97335-6|pages=第222-224頁}}{{en}}</ref><ref name="Raugh2004">{{cite book|author=Harold E. Raugh|title=''The Victorians at War, 1815-1914: An Encyclopedia of British Military History''| url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HvE_Pa_ZlfsC&pg=PA321| year=2004年| publisher=ABC-CLIO| isbn=978-1-57607-925-6|pages=第321–322,152頁}}{{en}}</ref>1904年[[英國侵藏戰爭|英國侵藏戰爭]]可能拍下了崗巴宗最早的照片。

[[File:Khamba_Dzong,_north_of_Everest,_1921.jpg|thumb]]
{{link-en|1921年珠穆朗瑪峰英國探路遠征|1921 British Mount Everest reconnaissance expedition}}是登山史上第一次探測[[珠穆朗瑪峰|珠穆朗瑪峰]]登頂的路線。英國登山隊從[[拉薩|拉薩]]出發，經過崗巴宗、[[協格爾鎮|協格爾鎮]]到[[崗嘎鎮|崗嘎鎮]]設立登山大本營。登山隊的{{link-en|Alexander Kellas|Alexander Kellas}}醫生因心臟病發而死，葬於崗巴宗以南小山上。<ref>{{Cite book | url=http://www.gutenberg.org/files/39421/39421-h/39421-h.htm#Page_54 | author=Howard-Bury, C. K. | year=1922 | title=''Mount Everest the Reconnaissance, 1921'' | edition=1 ed. | location=New York | publisher=Longman & Green | access-date=2017-10-11 | archive-date=2018-03-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180324150725/http://www.gutenberg.org/files/39421/39421-h/39421-h.htm#Page_54 | dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref>此次登上了[[章子峰|章子峰]]通往珠穆朗瑪峰的{{link-en|北坳|North col}}，但沒有嘗試登頂。

